# Sleep Tracker API

This is a REST API for tracking sleep periods (e.g. for a toddler) for multiple people.
A person may have multiple sleep periods, and all sleep periods belong to one person.

## People Collection [/people]

### List All People [GET]

Lists all people, their names, birthdays, and ID numbers.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "birthdate": "1999-05-02",
                "created_at": "2019-11-26T00:27:49.364Z",
                "id": 20,
                "name": "John Sample",
                "updated_at": "2019-11-26T00:27:49.364Z"
            },
            {
                "birthdate": "2004-08-31",
